## About me

- Working style: push back on my assumptions; propose advanced thinking; future-proof solutions; quality before speed; build one thing at a time.
- Non-negotiables: ikigai-aligned products; heart-centric thinking; attribution to framework originators always.
- On any pstack session: read ~/.config/pstack/last-session.md before suggesting next steps; run /pstack-help to surface the right next action.
